{"tid":1712940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]中大最後撤退計劃","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:24:01.000Z","uid":304886,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"88dfabadf9610aebd64f71102f9560a21374eaac","tid":1712940,"uid":304886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"既然都用得火，最後真係頂唔順可以一嘢燒曬campus入面嘅野，留俾啲狗一個著左火嘅campus<br />\nCampus啲設施都係死物，但係手足拉一個就小一個，最後真係吾得嗰陣就燒曬佢等啲狗得唔到佢哋想要嘅嘢<br />\n仲有中大出入口肯定吾止一條路<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtTzFSc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtTzFSc.png&h=c926285a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熟中大嘅人就知有其他小路走<br />\n希望最後吾洗用到呢招，但係見到手足俾狗圍攻真係好心庝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天佑中大</span></span>"},{"pid":"7be5cfa5ac8c921c0962e203bed9e4badf08976f","tid":1712940,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦P牌戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a133cb3295d52e2c325b6b9beef09763321638c5","tid":1712940,"uid":304886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be5cfa5ac8c921c0962e203bed9e4badf08976f","tid":1712940,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦P牌戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"咩叫最後？你有冇考慮有頂吾住既時候？中大入面開始缺物資同缺人，如果真係俾人攻到吾通係入面等死？"},{"pid":"49491ae280c809541f5f141b87e2c985b8f7a1d4","tid":1712940,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a133cb3295d52e2c325b6b9beef09763321638c5","tid":1712940,"uid":304886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7be5cfa5ac8c921c0962e203bed9e4badf08976f","tid":1712940,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦P牌戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-1